JOIN LIFE. UPCYCLED OUTERWEAR COLLECTION. Collected plastic is sorted by quality so it can be recycled correctly. PET, the material used in water bottles, is recovered and transformed into upcycled polyester.
#recovering #reusing #recycling #upcycling Thank you @s_blomqvist and @iamugbad
